---
title: “Croque Monsieur” Breakfast Strata with Prosciutto & Caramelized Onion
description: A strata is a baked egg and bread casserole that makes for an effortlessly indulgent breakfast. With mix-ins providing infinite variations, our strata takes a cue from the French, upgrading regular bread for cubes of sweet, buttery brioche that crisp up as they bake. Baked into the brioche and eggs are caramelized onion, umami-rich prosciutto, and melty white cheddar that browns to perfection. The addition of Dijon mustard and nutmeg complete the picture to create a morning meal that is simply parfait.

*This recipe is triple the typical servings, providing 6 servings and 12 servings for a 2 person and 4 person box respectively.*
